---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import mbbsImg from "@assets/img/mbbs.jpg";
---

<section>
  <div class="united-stats-area pt-120">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="united-states">
            <style>
              .text-center {
                text-align: center !important;
              }

              .tab-pane {
                display: none;
              }
              .tab-pane.active {
                display: block;
              }
              .nav-tabs {
                flex-direction: column;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link {
                border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
                border-radius: 0.25rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link.active {
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: white;
              }
            </style>

            <h2 class="united-states__title mb-15">Studying MBBS Abroad: Eligibility, Colleges, Fees, and Examinations</h2>

            <p>
              Studying MBBS abroad (Bachelor of Medicine, Bachelor of Surgery) is becoming increasingly popular among Indian students. In India, MBBS seats are very few, and many students fight for
              them.
            </p>
            <p>
              This makes it difficult for many students to get admission. As a result, many Indian candidates prefer to study MBBS abroad, believing that their chances of admission will be higher.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-30">
              They also believe that studying MBBS abroad will give them better chances of working around the world as a doctor. This trend reflects how Indian students are searching beyond their
              country for better education and employment opportunities in medicine.
            </p>

            <h3 >Reasons that attract students to study MBBS Abroad:</h3>

            <ul class="mb-30">
              <li style="list-style-type: disc;">Here you get access to enroll in top tier medical education programs</li>
              <li style="list-style-type: disc;">Here you get the opportunity to learn with experienced international faculty</li>
              <li style="list-style-type: disc;">There is ample exposure to medical technology and facilities</li>
              <li style="list-style-type: disc;">There is a multicultural atmosphere which makes the global perspective stronger</li>
              <li style="list-style-type: disc;">Possibility of studying in globally recognized renowned universities</li>
              <li style="list-style-type: disc;">International students get scholarships and financial help</li>
              <li style="list-style-type: disc;">Opportunity to do internship in prominent hospitals when they provide practical training</li>
            </ul>
            
          </div>
          <div class="cta-wrap" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: start;">
            <span class="col-6 theme-btn" style="margin-right: 20px;">Read More</span>
            <span class="col-6 theme-btn2">Get Assistance</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <Image src={mbbsImg} alt="Australia Image" width="600" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
